- 0.2.0

* You can now pass query options to get/push/set, etc.
* The old syntax no longer works. You now need to create instance variables of Firebase
* You can use the gem, '[firebase_token_generator](https://github.com/firebase/firebase-token-generator-ruby)', with this library.
  * Conflict with 'Fireabse' namespace is dissolved.

- 0.1.6

* You can now create instances of Firebase. The old syntax still works but will be removed in version 0,2. - @wannabefro
